      "value": {
        "latex": "Chercher le reste de la division euclidienne de\n$(X+1)^n - X^n - 1$ par $X^2 + X + 1$.",
        "html": "<p>Chercher le reste de la division euclidienne de <span class=\"math inline\">\\((X+1)^n - X^n - 1\\)</span> par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X^2 + X + 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "29e113a6-27de-4546-a873-7083dda6beec",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Substituer $j$ {\\`a} $X$ $ \\Rightarrow $\n         $R = \\begin{cases}(-1)^n - 2           &\\text{ si }n \\equiv 0 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, 3) \\hfill\\cr\n                     ((-1)^{n+1}-1)(X+1)  &\\text{ si }n \\equiv 1 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, 3) \\hfill\\cr\n                     ((-1)^n+1)X          &\\text{ si }n \\equiv 2 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, 3).\\end{cases}$",
        "html": "<p>Substituer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(j\\)</span> <span>à</span> <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Rightarrow\\)</span> <span class=\"math inline\">\\(R = \\begin{cases}(-1)^n - 2           &amp;\\text{ si }n \\equiv 0 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, 3) \\hfill\\cr\n                     ((-1)^{n+1}-1)(X+1)  &amp;\\text{ si }n \\equiv 1 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, 3) \\hfill\\cr\n                     ((-1)^n+1)X          &amp;\\text{ si }n \\equiv 2 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, 3).\\end{cases}\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
